otographs allowed the quality of the illustrations in this edition to be improved significantly.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aArchitect-designed houseszSwitzerlandzVevey. 0aArchitecture, DomesticzSwitzerland. 0aArchitecture, Domestic. 0aSmall housesvSwitzerland. 4aLe Corbusier. 4aVilla Le Lac. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh1 aFondation Le Corbusier, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMorel Journel, Guillemette.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2020z9783110704679oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303562065840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303562070240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035620702423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783035620702.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020